<p><img title="2.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/d172f2f57e5843e8a87d499e565b5d7a.jpg"></p>
<p><img title="3.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/533a8e3fca354eda96bd8ec50e30f295.jpg"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><a href="images/7b07e831084e4181a483789aa8ffabe1.jpg" target="_blank"><img title="4.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/7b07e831084e4181a483789aa8ffabe1.jpg"></a><a href="images/6b9bc4b3a63b41a7bab5259a39d96f05.jpg" target="_blank"><img title="5.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/6b9bc4b3a63b41a7bab5259a39d96f05.jpg"></a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span>学校食堂工作人员提前做好场地规划与设置，精心准备各类物资。家长、老师与孩子们一起动手，擀面皮、包饺子，在这个过程中，让孩子们真切地体会到了劳动的幸福、合作的快乐、分享的美好、团队的力量。</span></p>
<p><span><a href="images/4516cf06ebee4aa4b10bb0119ffce3f3.jpg" target="_blank"><img title="6.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/4516cf06ebee4aa4b10bb0119ffce3f3.jpg"></a><a href="images/ea0f66dd44164a7fb4a7d989bd6319df.jpg" target="_blank"><img title="7.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/ea0f66dd44164a7fb4a7d989bd6319df.jpg"></a></span></p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p><span>在团队花样比拼环节，主要考验各个团队队员的默契及队员们的动手能力，各代表队都不甘示弱。八仙过海，各显神通。一份份匠心独处的作品，都是同学们与老师家长的共同努力的成果。</span></p>
<p><span>评委团从团队协作、外观形状与整体造型、创新设计等多个方面进行现场打分。经过激烈角逐，最终评选出了花式饺子比赛最具潜力、最佳默契、最具颜值、最具效率等奖项，一起来看看部分成果展示吧</span><span>！</span></p>
<p><span><a href="images/371d558b59134595a41cafc92b48dd7f.jpg" target="_blank"><img title="8.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/371d558b59134595a41cafc92b48dd7f.jpg"></a><a href="images/e9ad0b83e9574c86af38173524b8e7c2.jpg" target="_blank"><img title="9.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/e9ad0b83e9574c86af38173524b8e7c2.jpg"></a><a href="images/4bd0cbcb68dc4f34b6d6bbcba44762ee.jpg" target="_blank"><img title="10.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/4bd0cbcb68dc4f34b6d6bbcba44762ee.jpg"></a><img title="11.jpg" src="/uploads/migration/images/68dae2f726da41a5ba88e978a8116561.jpg"></span><br></p>
<p><span></span></p>
<section>
 <section>
  <section>
   <section>
    <section>
     <p><span>严严冬日、感谢有你，情谊永驻人心</span></p>
    </section>
   </section>
  </section>
  <section>
   <section>
    <section>
     <section></section>
    </section>
   </section>
  </section>
  <section>
